      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to hit the road in style with this fantastic vehicle! It's in good, well-maintained condition and offers a smooth, reliable driving experience that you're sure to love. While it has been enjoyed and shows minor signs of careful use, it remains a clean and dependable choice for any driver looking for quality and value!",
